O

omitsDebugInformation() - Method in class org.ejvm.compilation.EjvmCompiler
Returns true if the compiler will omit debug information from the executable compiled.
org.ejvm.antlr - package org.ejvm.antlr
Contains the Java classes generated for the eJVM compiler by ANTLR.
org.ejvm.compilation - package org.ejvm.compilation
The compilation package contains classes important for the compilation of eJVM programs, most notably the implementation of the eJVM compiler itself.
org.ejvm.execution - package org.ejvm.execution
Contains classes used to execute compiled eJVM bytecode.
org.ejvm.frontend - package org.ejvm.frontend
Contains frontends for the usage of the eJVM Development Kit as well as the execution of compiled eJVM programs.
org.ejvm.inspection - package org.ejvm.inspection
Provides classes to inspect compiled eJVM bytecode.
org.ejvm.util - package org.ejvm.util
Contains helper and utility classes used in the eJVM Development Kit.
